<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. &quot;Krista leh Sapchuom di'n&quot; Aw suoh hitiu,
 I Lalpen uh deihum min chuh chawian hitiu;
 Lawptak in hat tawpin A na sem hitiu,
 Dikna lalgam a di'n theihtawp suoh hitiu.

[V2]
 Tanpa deihum, Krista di'n,
 Hukdampa, Krista di'n;
 Thisan a A chawk, Sapchuom di'n,
 Lalpa hatna ei pie'n.

[V3]
 2. &quot;Krista leh Sapchuom di'n&quot; paucham hitiu,
 A puonlap zui hitiu, nicheng a Kross chuh pu'n;
 Thagau Thieng hatna ah kipumpiek hitiu,
 Damsung chenga ginuma A na semin.

[V4]
 3. &quot;Krista leh Sapchuom di'n&quot; paucham hitiu,
 Phat leh theihna leh I sumuh Hukdampa di'n;
 I neih pha penuh Amah dingin piei tiu,
 Lunggil hehpihna tuoi thei ngeilo pumin.

[V5]
 4. &quot;Krista leh Sapchuom di'n&quot; paihvek hitiu,
 Mihinna, lauhna, chapona, Amah ziekin;
 I lungtup in I damsung hun hihnuom hen,
 Kipakin ei sapna achun chieh hitiu.</lyrics>
<title>FOR CHRISTAND THE CHURCH</title>
<hymn_number>268</hymn_number>
</song>